This paper discusses the design and implementation of a platform for blockchain interoperability and programmability, which involves topics related to cryptography, distributed computing, software engineering, programming languages, and compilers. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
